  • Need a space to have a party outside with shade, an aluminum retractable patio gazebo garden pergola with a weather-resistant canopy is the perfect solution. It offers privacy and optimal shade from harsh sun rays - simply slide the convertible top back and forth to suit your comfort level. The frame is made of durable rust-resistant powder-coated aluminum. The adjustable canopy provides for a welcome retreat on the hottest sunny days. This outdoor pergola kit can be used for all four seasons for year-round backyard beauty.

    What's Included?

    • Canopy
    • Anchor/Mounting Materials

    Features

    • Premium Material: Unlike other outdoor aluminum traditional Pergola with Canopies come with only 3 posts, our Aluminum post is 3.5in, with the thick pole our aluminum Pergola with Canopy is more sturdy than others. Our metal pergola with canopy has better wind resistance and snow-bearing capacity compared with other outdoor pergolas. Instead of using a 180g polyester canopy which is easy to tear apart or color-fading, this pergola gazebo is equipped with a thicker canopy with reinforced PA coating for better waterproof, UV-resistant as well as color-fading-resistant concerns. Protect your furniture from over-sunshine and heavy rain.
    • Retractable canopy: For the sake of convenience, the Aluminum Retractable Patio Gazebo Garden Pergola is adjustable, and canvas slides open or closed from both sides. It can be folded up and moved easily with the pulley on the inside of the canopy. You can unfold it for shade or put it away to enjoy the sunlight. Unlike the traditional outdoor metal pergola that uses ties to fix, the sunshade canopy is designed as removable and retractable with a magnetic catch on one side for you to easily open and close depending on your personal needs. The combination of two beautiful gray colors is unique.
    • Sturdy structure: Powder-coated aluminum frame is rust-resistant, strong, and durable. The pergola can be fixed on the ground for sturdy installation with stakes (stakes included), you can also fix it to your deck with extra anchoring.
    • Available size: This outdoor pergola with canopy comes in two option sizes: 10x10/10x13 pergola with canopy. You can select them according to your need.
    • Unique color: Unlike traditional pergolas in gray and beige, our pergola combines two different gray colors to make the pergola more beautiful and unique.
    • Clear installation steps: Just follow the assembly guide video step by step, it is quick to finish the installation and get your new Steel Retractable Pergola Gazebo.
